Hello, thank you for calling the Harmony Music School! My name is Bruce Bell. May I have your name, please?

Hi Bruce, my name is Jane Kelly. I'm so excited to start lessons!

Nice to meet you, Jane! We're thrilled to have you on board. To set up your account, could you please provide me with your email address?

Sure thing! It's janekelly at email dot com.

Thanks, Jane. And could you also provide me with your phone number, just in case we need to reach you quickly?

Certainly! It's five five five, one two three, four five six seven.

Perfect, thank you. We take your privacy seriously and ensure your information is secure.

That's great to hear, Bruce. I can't wait to get started with my lessons.

We're excited to have you, Jane! If you have any questions, feel free to reach out. Thank you for joining Harmony Music School!

Thank you, Bruce! Looking forward to it!

Thank you for your time, Jane. Have a wonderful day!
